{"tid":253253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港女發火】兇走MK仔港女：唔驚俾人尋仇","createTime":"2017-05-22T09:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T16:56:44.000Z","uid":5591,"like":81,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49e1a36aac998a668ab873552c9e016c527b183a","tid":253253,"uid":5591,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"識食一定係呢d熱褲港嬸！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170520/large/1495268018_531d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170520%2Flarge%2F1495268018_531d.jpg&h=9960b0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_512910_0&amp;i=20170522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_512910_0%26i%3D20170522&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7BywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6760e3cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_512910_0%26i%3D20170522&h=59eaba4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_512910_0&amp;i=20170522</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「當時沒想這麽多，我只知想幫他(被欺負男子)，想趕走那兩名男子。」《壹週刊》找到發火趕走MK仔的港女，原來她是曾做𡃁模的Yo Yo。 <br />\n<br />\nYo Yo表示，她並不認識片段中三名男子，只認得孖煙囪男跟他在同一酒吧消遣，當時已喝醉。Yo Yo跟朋友在嘉芙中心門口吹風時，看到兩名MK仔欺負醉酒的孖煙囪男。 <br />\n<br />\n「見到兩名男子正在欺負一名男子，(他們是否認識？)他們應該不認識的。我望過去時，我看到他們弄他的乳頭，扯他的褲子。又拍他的照片。所以我就衝過去，企圖叫他們(MK仔)不要再玩，怎知被他們罵。」 <br />\n<br />\n罵你什麼？「他們罵我是阿嬸，都是講粗口的，問候母親那些。之後又說：『阿嬸，關你什麼事呀？』對罵的，之後他們就(向我)擲玻璃樽，不知是否想嚇我，我就執起塊玻璃(指向他)。」兩名MK仔見Yo Yo發惡，只好離去。 <br />\n<br />\n當是有否害怕？「當時沒想這麽多，我只知想幫他(被欺負男子)。想趕走那兩名男子。我走回去時，就叫他離開，就拉他走，替他穿回褲子。」<br />\n<br />\n當時會否擔心對方打你？「因為我本身的性格，一向喜歡保護弱小的人，因為是獅子座。我想在尖沙咀的大街，又這麽多閉路電視，應該不會對我做什麼的。」會否擔心被人尋仇？「我又沒想過，當時更加不會這樣想，因一心想幫人。」 <br />\n<br />\n幫人是好，但也要考慮當時的實際情況。最好的，還是報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n撰文：程志康 <br />\n<br />\n攝影：海江田"},{"pid":"3f8cc6dd4165d85ff086f2bdef8797c957ed8664","tid":253253,"uid":79471,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母星座撚 心口又有十字架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n異教徒?"},{"pid":"985c52562b84ed354617eaed07db195f62a62b84","tid":253253,"uid":92498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26d0100c2695e798ec60d6b3cd5fe4d24b023a0c","tid":253253,"uid":25204,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"比人罵啊嬸即有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec0df0e8f3a8fda6a387b941b8bc8cfe09b0522","tid":253253,"uid":63950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"005978ad3e761aeed8ad11512c06e08b3af2aae2","tid":253253,"uid":111955,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"起碼好過只拍片既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8195f29a0010e7e78bb7edd7e52ddc4cb9102b7","tid":253253,"uid":7796,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"因為是獅子座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係on9星座撚"},{"pid":"17011ad284501fefeb1a031dbf8a924486198527","tid":253253,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"多謝報紙佬登曬條女個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93da030a9f64220975b335185456b2eb30e4a8b0","tid":253253,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝報紙佬登曬條女個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢不知幾想"},{"pid":"f7a5f7bc2de4e70c6d9c5484490b1aa598f983c0","tid":253253,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017